> <span begin="00:28.264" end="00:28.507">mine</span> <span begin="00:28.507" end="00:28.658">is</span> <span begin="00:28.658" end="00:28.882">bet</span><span begin="00:28.940" end="00:29.748">ter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">相信我 我的经历更惨痛</span></p><p begin="00:31.442" end="00:35.114" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:31.442" end="00:31.629">We're</span> <span begin="00:31.629" end="00:32.066">so</span> <span begin="00:32.066" end="00:32.932">young,</span> <span begin="00:33.315" end="00:33.427">but</span> <span begin="00:33.427" end="00:33.599">we're</span> <span begin="00:33.651" end="00:33.909">on</span> <span begin="00:33.909" end="00:34.158">the</span> <span begin="00:34.158" end="00:34.372">road</span> <span begin="00:34.372" end="00:34.548">to</span> <span begin="00:34.548" end="00:34.909">ru</span><span begin="00:34.909" end="00:35.114">in</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们正值花季 却已走上毁灭之路</span></p><p begin="00:35.365" end="00:39.065" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:35.365" end="00:35.572">We</span> <span begin="00:35.572" end="00:35.971">play</span> <span begin="00:36.052" end="00:36.665">dumb,</span> <span begin="00:36.819" end="00:36.922">but</span> <span begin="00:36.922" end="00:37.090">we</span> <span begin="00:37.090" end="00:37.347">know</span> <span begin="00:37.347" end="00:37.523">ex</span><span begin="00:37.523" end="00:37.840">act</span><span begin="00:37.840" end="00:38.027">ly</span> <span begin="00:38.093" end="00:38.294">what</span> <span begin="00:38.333" end="00:38.535">we're</span> <span begin="00:38.577" end="00:38.808">do</span><span begin="00:38.808" end="00:39.065">ing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们佯装无知 但其实心知肚明</span></p><p begin="00:39.300" end="00:42.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:39.300" end="00:39.485">We</span> <span begin="00:39.485" end="00:39.973">cry</span> <span begin="00:39.973" end="00:40.706">tear</span><span begin="00:40.706" end="00:40.911">s</span> <span begin="00:41.116" end="00:41.282">of</span> <span begin="00:41.282" end="00:41.533">mas</span><span begin="00:41.533" end="00:41.989">cara</span> <span begin="00:42.018" end="00:42.211">in</span> <span begin="00:42.255" end="00:42.357">the</span> <span begin="00:42.385" end="00:42.629">ba</span><span begin="00:42.629" end="00:42.746">th</span><span begin="00:42.746" end="00:42.940">room</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在洗手间里 泪水混着睫毛膏滑落</span></p><p begin="00:42.966" end="00:45.341" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:42.966" end="00:43.183">Hon</span><span begin="00:43.183" end="00:43.360">ey,</span> <span begin="00:43.385" end="00:43.533">li</span><span begin="00:43.533" end="00:43.681">fe</span> <span begin="00:43.767" end="00:43.985">is</span> <span begin="00:43.985" end="00:44.202">just</span> <span begin="00:44.202" end="00:44.331">a</span> <span begin="00:44.331" end="00:44.745">class</span><span begin="00:44.745" end="00:45.341">room</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">亲爱的 生活不过是一间教室</span></p><p begin="00:45.627" end="00:48.063" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:45.627" end="00:45.964">Ah-</span><span begin="00:45.964" end="00:46.212">ah-</span><span begin="00:46.212" end="00:46.443">ah-</span><span begin="00:46.443" end="00:46.658">ah,</span> <span begin="00:46.685" end="00:47.023">ah,</span> <span begin="00:47.179" end="00:48.063">ah</span></p><p begin="00:48.567" end="00:52.323" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:48.567" end="00:48.902">'Cause,</span> <span begin="00:48.902" end="00:49.414">baby,</span> <span begin="00:49.414" end="00:49.613">I</span> <span begin="00:49.658" end="00:49.879">could</span> <span begin="00:49.924" end="00:50.114">build</span> <span begin="00:50.114" end="00:50.312">a</span> <span begin="00:50.361" end="00:50.858">cas</span><span begin="00:50.858" end="00:52.323">tle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为宝贝 我可以筑起一座城堡</span></p><p begin="00:52.774" end="00:56.303" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:52.774" end="00:53.107">Out</span> <span begin="00:53.107" end="00:53.317">of</span> <span begin="00:53.317" end="00:53.588">all</span> <span begin="00:53.588" end="00:53.768">the</span> <span begin="00:53.836" end="00:54.089">bricks</span> <span begin="00:54.089" end="00:54.283">they</span> <span begin="00:54.340" end="00:54.568">threw</span> <span begin="00:54.568" end="00:54.773">at</span> <span begin="00:54.824" end="00:56.303">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">用他们丢向我的所有砖块</span></p><p begin="00:56.506" end="00:59.999" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:56.506" end="00:56.765">And</span> <span begin="00:56.765" end="00:57.016">eve</span><span begin="00:57.016" end="00:57.209">ry</span> <span begin="00:57.253" end="00:57.517">day</span> <span begin="00:57.517" end="00:57.759">is</span> <span begin="00:57.759" end="00:58.038">like</span> <span begin="00:58.038" end="00:58.201">a</span> <span begin="00:58.245" end="00:58.628">bat</span><span begin="00:58.675" end="00:59.999">tle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每天都像一场战役</span></p><p begin="01:00.444" end="01:03.555" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:00.444" end="01:00.686">But</span> <span begin="01:00.686" end="01:00.947">eve</span><span begin="01:00.947" end="01:01.159">ry</span> <span begin="01:01.194" end="01:01.437">night</span> <span begin="01:01.437" end="01:01.688">with</span> <span begin="01:01.688" end="01:01.958">us</span> <span begin="01:01.958" end="01:02.188">is</span> <span begin="01:02.188" end="01:02.427">like</span> <span begin="01:02.427" end="01:02.596">a</span> <span begin="01:02.654" end="01:03.555">dream</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但每晚我们在一起都恍如梦境</span></p><p begin="01:03.634" end="01:05.357" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:03.634" end="01:03.893">Baby,<