.625" end="01:11.777">are</span> <span begin="01:11.777" end="01:12.043">too</span> <span begin="01:12.043" end="01:12.444">busy</span> <span begin="01:12.484" end="01:12.830">danc</span><span begin="01:12.830" end="01:13.119">ing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们沉迷热舞</span></p><p begin="01:13.370" end="01:15.146" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:13.370" end="01:13.503">To</span> <span begin="01:13.503" end="01:13.684">get</span> <span begin="01:13.735" end="01:14.011">knocked</span> <span begin="01:14.011" end="01:14.169">of</span><span begin="01:14.226" end="01:14.289">f</span> <span begin="01:14.289" end="01:14.440">our</span> <span begin="01:14.472" end="01:14.989">fee</span><span begin="01:14.989" end="01:15.146">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不让任何困境将我们击垮</span></p><p begin="01:15.458" end="01:17.057" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:15.458" end="01:15.690">Baby,</span> <span begin="01:15.690" end="01:15.837">we're</span> <span begin="01:15.837" end="01:15.958">the</span> <span begin="01:15.958" end="01:16.200">new</span> <span begin="01:16.200" end="01:16.384">ro</span><span begin="01:16.419" end="01:16.653">man</span><span begin="01:16.694" end="01:16.919">ti</span><span begin="01:16.919" end="01:17.057">cs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宝贝 我们是新一代浪漫主义者</span></p><p begin="01:17.194" end="01:20.265" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:17.194" end="01:17.360">The</span> <span begin="01:17.440" end="01:17.881">best</span> <span begin="01:17.908" end="01:18.180">peo</span><span begin="01:18.180" end="01:18.418">ple</span> <span begin="01:18.418" end="01:18.651">in</span> <span begin="01:18.651" end="01:19.064">li</span><span begin="01:19.161" end="01:19.271">fe</span> <span begin="01:19.271" end="01:19.376">are</span> <span begin="01:19.409" end="01:20.265">free</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">生活中最美好的人都自由无羁</span></p><p begin="01: